      .inner
        p(itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/numberOfPlayers") A party game where you and your friends struggle to defend the the stupid statements given to you. 
        |  It is playable on any device with a modern browser, and supports 
        span(itemprop="minValue") 3
        | -
        span(itemprop="maxValue") 8 
